quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,171,WE ‘IDH NETEKNAL-XHEBELE FEWKAHUM KE’ENNEHU DHULLETUN WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHU WAKI’UN BIHIM HUDHU MA ‘ATEJNAKUM BIKUWETIN WE EDHKURU MA FIHI LE’ALLEKUM TETTEKUNE
  7,172,WE ‘IDH ‘EHADHE REBBUKE MIN BENI ‘ADEME MIN DHUHURIHIM DHURRIJETEHUM WE ‘ESH/HEDEHUM ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIHIM ‘ELESTU BIREBBIKUM KALU BELA SHEHIDNA ‘EN TEKULU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNA KUNNA ‘AN HADHA GAFILINE
  7,173,‘EW TEKULU ‘INNEMA ‘ESHREKE ‘ABA’UUNA MIN KABLU WE KUNNA DHURRIJETEN MIN BA’DIHIM ‘EFETUHLIKUNA BIMA FE’ALEL-MUBTILUNE
  7,174,WE KEDHELIKE NUFESSILUL-’AJATI WE LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  7,175,WE ETLU ‘ALEJHIM NEBE’EL-LEDHI ‘ATEJNAHU ‘AJATINA FANSELEHA MINHA FE’ETBE’AHU ESH-SHEJTANU FEKANE MINEL-GAWINE
  7,176,WE LEW SHI’NA LEREFA’NAHU BIHA WE LEKINNEHU ‘EHLEDE ‘ILAL-’ERDI WE ETTEBE’A HEWAHU FEMETHELUHU KEMETHELIL-KELBI ‘IN TEHMIL ‘ALEJHI JELHETH ‘EW TETRUK/HU JELHETH DHALIKE METHELUL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FAKSUSIL-KASESE LE’ALLEHUM JETEFEKKERUNE
  7,177,SA’E METHELÆNL-KAWMUL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA WE ‘ENFUSEHUM KANU JEDHLIMUNE
  7,178,MEN JEHDI ELLAHU FEHUWEL-MUHTEDI WE MEN JUDLIL FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  7,179,WE LEKAD DHERE’NA LIXHEHENNEME KETHIRÆN MINEL-XHINNI WEL-’INSI LEHUM KULUBUN LA JEFKAHUNE BIHA WE LEHUM ‘A’JUNUN LA JUBSIRUNE BIHA WE LEHUM ‘ADHANUN LA JESMA’UNE BIHA ‘ULA’IKE KAL’EN’AMI BEL HUM ‘EDELLU ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-GAFILUNE
  7,180,WE LILLEHIL-’ESMA’UL-HUSNA FAD’UHU BIHA WE DHERUL-LEDHINE JULHIDUNE FI ‘ESMA’IHI SEJUXHZEWNE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  7,181,WE MIMMEN HALEKNA ‘UMMETUN JEHDUNE BIL-HEKKI WE BIHI JA’DILUNE
  7,182,WEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA SENESTEDRIXHUHUM MIN HEJTHU LA JA’LEMUNE
  7,183,WE ‘UMLI LEHUM ‘INNE KEJDI METINUN
  7,184,‘EWELEM JETEFEKKERU MA BISAHIBIHIM MIN XHINNETIN ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  7,185,‘EWELEM JENDHURU FI MELEKUTI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA HALEKAL-LAHU MIN SHEJ’IN WE ‘EN ‘ASA ‘EN JEKUNE KADI EKTEREBE ‘EXHELUHUM FEBI’EJJI HEDITHIN BA’DEHU JU’UMINUNE
  7,186,MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FELA HADIJE LEHU WE JEDHERUHUM FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  7,187,JES’ELUNEKE ‘ANI ES-SA’ATI ‘EJJANE MURSAHA KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ILMUHA ‘INDE RABBI LA JUXHELLIHA LIWEKTIHA ‘ILLA HUWE THEKULET FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI LA TE’TIKUM ‘ILLA BEGTETEN JES’ELUNEKE KE’ENNEKE HEFIJUN ‘ANHA KUL ‘INNEMA ‘ILMUHA ‘INDEL-LAHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTH
  7,188,KUL LA ‘EMLIKU LINEFSI NEF’ÆN WE LA DERRÆN ‘ILLA MA SHA’EL-LAHU WE LEW KUNTU ‘A’LEMUL-GAJBE LASTEKTHERTU MINEL-HAJRI WE MA MESSENIJE ES-SU’U ‘IN ‘ENA ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN WE BESHIRUN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE